title: Beautiful Duplex Up with Huge Atrium and private roof deck
posting_body: Giant 3 bedroom with 3 bath penthouse duplex in the best neighborhood in Chicago!!!

Large kitchen (stainless, granite, wine cooler, glass vent hood, dw, garbage disposal), 30 foot atrium with windows from top to bottom, very high 12 foot ceilings with crown moldings, hardwood floors with inlays, loft with a wet-bar (w/wine cooler), master bedroom w/ private balcony, master bath w/ jacuzzi, separate frameless shower w/body spray, 2nd bedroom with private balcony and jacuzzi, in-unit washer and dryer, central heat/air, private garage and to top it all off your own PRIVATE ROOF-TOP DECK with the best view in Chicago!
You will be 1 block from: blue line and cab stand, 3 blocks from interstate and within walking distance to shopping, groceries, bars, restaurants, etc.
Please call Scott with questions or to see 773-647-6765
